<lb n="0913c04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0913012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，（佛說）＋智【元】【明】</note><note n="0913012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智【大】，佛說智【元】【明】，【原】麗本</note><app n="0913012"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">佛說智</rdg></app><note n="0913012" type="rest" place="foot">【原】麗本</note>炬陀羅尼<note n="0913013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＋（與趙宋施護出智光滅業障經同本）十四字【元】【明】，但明本無本字</note><note n="0913013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經與趙宋施護出智光滅業障經同本【元】，經與趙宋施護出智光滅業障經同【明】</note><app n="0913013"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">經與趙宋施護出智光滅業障經同本</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">經與趙宋施護出智光滅業障經同</rdg></app><note n="0913014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【三】</note><note n="0913014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913014"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0913c05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0913c06" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">唐三藏法師提雲般若等奉　制譯</byline>
<lb n="0913c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0913c0701">如是我聞。一時佛在日月宮中。與無量大菩
<lb n="0913c08" ed="T"/>薩眾俱。普賢菩薩文殊師利菩薩。陀羅尼自
<lb n="0913c09" ed="T"/>在王菩薩執金剛菩薩。如是等菩薩摩訶薩
<lb n="0913c10" ed="T"/>而為上首。</p>
<lb n="0913c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0913c1101">爾時東方有佛號智炬如來。南方有佛。號金
<lb n="0913c12" ed="T"/>光聚如來。西方有佛號實語如來。北方有佛
<lb n="0913c13" ed="T"/>號雷音王如來。各從本國而來此會。</p>
<lb n="0913c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0913c1401">爾時世尊與諸如來及菩薩眾。共在金幢樓
<lb n="0913c15" ed="T"/>觀之中。各坐寶嚴師子之座。時日月天子來
<lb n="0913c16" ed="T"/>詣佛所。頭<note n="0913015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頂＝面【三】</note><note n="0913015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頂【大】，面【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913015"><lem wit="【大】">頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">面</rdg></app>禮敬諸佛菩薩。以眾妙物而
<lb n="0913c17" ed="T"/>為供養。供養畢已退坐一面。互相謂言。我等
<lb n="0913c18" ed="T"/>云何從諸如來及菩薩所。而得發起一切眾
<lb n="0913c19" ed="T"/>生光明破諸黑闇滿十方智<note n="0913016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔炬〕－【三】</note><note n="0913016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">炬【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913016"><lem wit="【大】">炬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>陀羅尼耶。以
<lb n="0913c20" ed="T"/>是陀羅尼力故。當令我等能為眾生作大明
<lb n="0913c21" ed="T"/>炬。說是語時。彼諸如來及菩薩眾。即共同聲
<lb n="0913c22" ed="T"/>而說呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0913c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0913c2301" cb:type="dharani">娑<note place="inline">借音即此字細內之上聲下但有字傍<note n="0913017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">注＝註【三】</note><note n="0913017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">注【大】，註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913017"><lem wit="【大】">注</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">註</rdg></app>上去<note n="0913018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音＝者【三】</note><note n="0913018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音【大】，者【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913018"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">者</rdg></app>皆倣此</note>野替<note place="inline"><note n="0913019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔音〕－【三】</note><note n="0913019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913019"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>他地<note n="0913020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝切【明】＊</note><note n="0913020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反【大】＊，切【明】＊</note><app n="0913020"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>談<note place="inline"><note n="0913021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔句〕－【明】＊</note><note n="0913021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">句【大】＊，〔－〕【明】＊</note><app n="0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一</note>
<lb n="0913c24" ed="T"/>斫芻<note place="inline"><note n="0913022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＋（聲）【明】＊</note><note n="0913022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】＊，上聲【明】＊</note><app n="0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>達陀<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>二</note>斫芻<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>鉢<note n="0913023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝邏【三】</note><note n="0913023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】，邏【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913023"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">邏</rdg></app>婆<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三</note>杜
<lb n="0913c25" ed="T"/>羅米他<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>四</note>迦<note place="inline">迦之上聲迦音紀伽<app type="star" corresp="#0913020"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>羅<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>他<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五</note>伊
<lb n="0913c26" ed="T"/><note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>替<note place="inline">他止<app type="star" corresp="#0913020"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>炭<note place="inline">他鄧<app type="star" corresp="#0913020"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>下同</note>娑<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>六</note>蘇<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>囉<note place="inline">依羅字本音而轉舌
<lb n="0913c27" ed="T"/>呼之<note n="0913024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪〕－【三】</note><note n="0913024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913024"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>內有口邊作魯<note n="0913025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梨＋（利）【三】</note><note n="0913025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梨【大】，梨利【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0913025"><lem wit="【大】">梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">梨利</rdg></app>履盧邏者皆倣此</note>吒<note place="inline">都假<app type="star" corresp="#0913020"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七</note>蘇<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>囉<note n="0913026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拕＝柁【三】＊</note><note n="0913026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拕【大】＊，柁【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0913026"><lem wit="【大】">拕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">柁</rdg></app><note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>八</note>
<lb n="0913c28" ed="T"/>蘇<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>哆<note place="inline">丁佐<app type="star" corresp="#0913020"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>娑<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>九</note>壹炭娑<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0913021"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>十</note>陛羅<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0913022"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>
